&lt;h1 id="find-your-specific-knowledge-through-action"&gt;Find Your Specific Knowledge Through Action&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Jul 29 2025&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I ultimately think that everyone should be figuring out what it is that they uniquely do best—that aligns with who they are fundamentally, and that gives them authenticity, that brings them specific knowledge, that gives them competitive advantage, that makes them irreplaceable. And they should just lean into that. And sometimes you don&amp;rsquo;t know what that is until you do it.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Desire Is a Contract You Make to Be Unhappy</title><link>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/desire-is-a-contract-you-make-to-be-unhappy/</link><pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2020 15:39:49 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/desire-is-a-contract-you-make-to-be-unhappy/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguage.github.io/naval/zh/desire-is-a-contract-you-make-to-be-unhappy.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
